body:
Hi Sarah,

Added belt-and-suspenders backend safeguard to match your frontend fix.

## What I Added

In both Events_Create and Events_Update:

```javascript
// If startDate and endDate span multiple calendar days
const startDay = startDate.toISOString().split('T')[0];
const endDay = endDate.toISOString().split('T')[0];
if (startDay !== endDay) {
    // Force non-repeating
    event.isRepeating = false;
    event.recurrenceRule = null;
}
```

## Behavior

- Multi-day events (like 3-day festivals) automatically get isRepeating=false
- Even if frontend accidentally sends isRepeating=true, backend will override
- Logs when this override happens for debugging

